<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .refund-details { background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .success-message { color: #4CAF50; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Recyleto Pharmacy</h1>
            <h2>Refund Approved!</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Valued Customer,</p>
            
            <p class="success-message">Great news! Your refund request has been approved.</p>
            
            <div class="refund-details">
                <h3>Refund Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Refund Reference:</strong> #<%= refund.reference %></p>
                <p><strong>Transaction Reference:</strong> #<%= refund.transactionReference %></p>
                <p><strong>Amount Refunded:</strong> ₦<%= refund.amount.toLocaleString() %></p>
                <p><strong>Approval Date:</strong> <%= new Date(refund.processedAt).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
                <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> Original payment method</p>
            </div>

            <p>The refund amount will be credited to your original payment method within 5-7 business days.</p>
            
            <p>If you don't see the refund in your account after this period, please contact your bank or payment provider.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your patience and for choosing Recyleto.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 Recyleto Pharmacy. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>